nodes.text: Chew-blubber was a food item served at the Canto Casino Hotel in the city of Canto Bight on the planet Cantonica. In 34 ABY, the salesbeing Kedpin Shoklop noticed chew-blubbers among the food served during midmeal at the Canto Casino Hotel.

Chew-blubber first appeared in the 2017 short story "Rules of the Game," written by Saladin Ahmed for the novella collection Canto Bight, released as part of the Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi multimedia project.
